Please read the files (especially INSTALL) in the
huskybse package FIRST!

Unix:
-----

0. the smapi and the fidoconfig package is required for the hpt package. They
   must be already compiled and installed.

   fidoconfig "stable" version is required.
   smapi "stable" version is required.

1. Put the hpt package in the directory where the other packages of fido
   linux reside:

   /usr/src/packages/        -> smapi/
                             -> fidoconf/
                             -> hpt/

2. compile smapi, fidoconf, hpt

You're ready. If you have a working config, you can now use fido under unix.
